                	<h2 class="page-title">Accomodation</h2>
                <!-- start main content -->
    <div class="entry"> 
   
  <p>FSCONS has made agreements which provides discounts for our visitors with the following hotels and hostels:</p>
<ul class="accomodation">
<li class="hotel"><a href="http://www.mornington.se/goteborg.aspx?pageId=1&amp;lang=2">Mornington Hotel Göteborg</a></li>
<ul>
<li class="hoteldescription">10% discount on Best Available Rate for single roomMention FSCONS 2008 when placing your order<a href="http://tinyurl.com/4clklb">Map with directions to ferry (Eniro.se)</a></li>
</ul>

<li class="hotel"><a href="http://www.hostel-gothenburg.com/">Hostelling International Stigbergsliden</a></li>
<ul>
<li class="hoteldescription">Member rates for stay in 3-8 bed roomsMention FSCONS 2008 when placing your order.<a href="http://tinyurl.com/4atgdh">Map with directions to ferry (Eniro.se)</a></li>
</ul>

</ul>
<p>We have also found that the following hostels, which all have websites, are not far from the ferry that takes you directly to the venue in four minutes:</p>
<ul class="accomodation">
<li class="hotel"><a href="http://www.goteborgsvandrarhem.se/en/">Göteborgs Vandrarhem</a></li>
<li class="hoteldescription"><a href="http://tinyurl.com/487zfh">Map with directions to bus (Eniro.se)</a>You can take trams #2 or #4 to Brunnsparken and change to bus #16 from there.</li>
<li class="hotel"><a href="http://slottsskogenvh.se">Slottsskogen Vandrarhem</a></li>
<li class="hoteldescription"><a href="http://tinyurl.com/47ft9p">Map with directions to ferry (Eniro.se)</a></li>
<li class="hotel"><a href="http://mastenvandrarhem.com">Masthuggsterrassens Vandrarhem</a></li>
<li class="hoteldescription"><a href="http://tinyurl.com/3f7v2v">&nbsp;Map with directions to ferry (Eniro.se)</a></li>
<li class="hotel"><a href="http://linnehostel.com/">Linn&#233; Hostel</a></li>
<li class="hoteldescription"><a href="http://tinyurl.com/47ft9p">Map with directions to ferry (Eniro.se)</a></li>
</ul>
   
